page.title: 16A DAY IN THE LIFE OF CLAIRE
page.content: I woke up at 6am and got dressed then I went to have breakfast.After breakfast my Dad and I went to church. We are Catholics and have to travel ten miles to our church.Then we went for a walk.We returned home at 9am.I went to empty the bin.Then I helped to do the washing up.In the afternoon my family went swimming in Shrewsbury baths four miles away.I went home with my family for tea.It was fish and chips.After tea I went to Brownies which meet in my local Primary school. At Brownies we went for a nature walk round the village.I found a caterpillar. We went back to the school and played some games.Then I went home.I watched television until 8.30pm when I went to bed.
